KPSC UI Manifesto & React Frontend Build Prompt

PART 1 — UI MANIFESTO
Product Identity
Kerala Public Service Commission Meeting & Agenda Management System.
Users are senior government officials, ministers, Joint Secretaries, and Additional Secretaries.
Age range: 40–70. Non-technical. High accountability. Low tolerance for ambiguity.

Core Design Principle: Consequential Clarity
Every interaction in this system carries administrative and legal weight.
The UI must make it impossible to be confused about:

What state an item is in
What action is available to you right now
Whether your action succeeded


