RULE: Never use green for a primary action button.
Green is reserved exclusively for CONSOLIDATED and WING_APPROVED status chips.
All primary action buttons use Blue (#1A4480) or Gold (#F0B429) only.
Gold buttons: used ONLY for the highest-stakes action per screen (e.g. "Finalize Sitting", "Final Decision").
Blue buttons: used for standard primary actions (Approve, Submit, Save).
Secondary/ghost buttons: white bg, 1px #D1D5DB border, dark text.
Destructive buttons (Return, Reject): white bg, 1px red border, red text — never filled red.

2. TYPOGRAPHY
Font stack: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif
Scale:
Page title (H1):    28px  weight 700  color #0F1F3D
Section title (H2): 20px  weight 600  color #0F1F3D
Card title (H3):    16px  weight 600  color #111827
Body:               15px  weight 400  color #374151
Secondary text:     13px  weight 400  color #6B7280
Label/chip text:    12px  weight 500  (uppercase for status chips only)
Button text:        14px  weight 600
Table header:       12px  weight 600  color #6B7280  UPPERCASE  letter-spacing 0.5px
Table cell:         14px  weight 400  color #111827
RULE: Minimum font size is 13px. No exceptions.
RULE: All interactive labels must have visible text. No icon-only buttons except within confirmed icon-labelled toolbars.

3. SPACING & SIZING
Touch/click targets: Minimum 44×44px for all interactive elements.
This means: table action buttons must be at least 44px tall with adequate padding.
Icon buttons: 40px × 40px box with 8px icon, NOT 20px × 20px box with 16px icon.
Page layout:

Sidebar: 240px fixed
Content: calc(100vw - 240px), max-width 1440px
Page padding: 32px horizontal, 28px vertical
Card gap: 16px
Section gap: 32px

Cards:

Background: #FFFFFF
Border: 1px solid #E5E7EB
Border-radius: 8px
Padding: 20px 24px
Hover state on clickable cards: border-color #1A4480, box-shadow 0 0 0 3px rgba(26,68,128,0.08)

Form fields:

Height: 44px (never shorter — this is a tap target)
Border: 1px solid #D1D5DB
Border-radius: 6px
Focus: 2px solid #1A4480 border, no box-shadow
Font size: 15px (not 13px, not 12px — 15px minimum for data entry)
Padding: 0 12px


