6. DATA TABLES
Use MUI DataGrid for all tabular data.
Required props for every DataGrid:
jsx<DataGrid
  rows={rows}
  columns={columns}
  pageSize={20}
  rowsPerPageOptions={[10, 20, 50]}
  disableSelectionOnClick
  autoHeight
  sx={{ border: 'none' }}
  components={{ Toolbar: CustomToolbar }}
/>
CustomToolbar must include:

Search input (debounced, 300ms)
Filter button (MUI GridToolbarFilterButton)
Export CSV button

Column rules:

Header: 12px uppercase, #6B7280, bold
Cell text: 14px, #111827
Row height: 56px minimum (NOT 52px — 44px content + 12px padding)
Hover row: bg #F8FAFF
Status column: ALWAYS renders a MUI Chip with the semantic colours above

Action column:
jsx// Minimum — never just icons
<Button size="small" startIcon={<VisibilityIcon/>} sx={{minWidth: 100}}>
  View
</Button>
Never: <IconButton><VisibilityIcon/></IconButton> alone.
Each action button must have a text label. The icon is decorative.

7. STATUS CHIPS
jsx// Standard status chip — use everywhere consistently
const StatusChip = ({ status }) => {
  const config = {
    DRAFT:                { label: 'Draft',            bg: '#F3F4F6', color: '#4B5563' },
    PENDING_WING_APPROVAL:{ label: 'Pending Approval', bg: '#FEF3C7', color: '#92400E' },
    WING_APPROVED:        { label: 'Wing Approved',    bg: '#DBEAFE', color: '#1E40AF' },
    PENDING_RNA:          { label: 'Pending R&A',      bg: '#EDE9FE', color: '#5B21B6' },
    CONSOLIDATED:         { label: 'Consolidated',     bg: '#D1FAE5', color: '#065F46' },
    FINALIZED:            { label: 'Finalized',        bg: '#FEF9C3', color: '#854D0E' },
    SUPPLEMENTARY:        { label: 'Supplementary',    bg: '#F3E8FF', color: '#6B21A8' },
    VOTED:                { label: 'Voted',            bg: '#DCFCE7', color: '#14532D' },
    CHAIRMAN_DECIDED:     { label: 'Decided',          bg: '#F0FDF4', color: '#166534' },
    RETURNED:             { label: 'Returned',         bg: '#FEE2E2', color: '#991B1B' },
    ARCHIVED:             { label: 'Archived',         bg: '#F1F5F9', color: '#475569' },
  };
  const c = config[status] || { label: status, bg: '#F3F4F6', color: '#4B5563' };
  return (
    <Chip
      label={c.label}
      size="small"
      sx={{
        backgroundColor: c.bg,
        color: c.color,
        fontWeight: 600,
        fontSize: '11px',
        height: '22px',
        '& .MuiChip-label': { px: 1.5 }
      }}
    />
  );
};

8. FORMS
All forms must use a multi-step stepper for more than 4 fields.
Single-page forms with 8+ fields cause anxiety for non-tech users.
Agenda creation uses a 3-step stepper:

Step 1: Select Meeting + Wing + Form Type
Step 2: Fill Agenda Details (topic, file number, description, discussion points)
Step 3: Attachments (upload PDFs, enter friendly names)

Stepper styling:
jsx<Stepper activeStep={step} sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
  <Step><StepLabel>Select Meeting</StepLabel></Step>
  <Step><StepLabel>Agenda Details</StepLabel></Step>
  <Step><StepLabel>Attachments</StepLabel></Step>
</Stepper>
Required field indicator: Red asterisk (*) next to label, never below input.
Error messages: Below the field in red, 13px. Never replace the label. Never use toast for inline validation errors.
Character count: Show for all textarea fields. Format: "47/500 characters".
Subject/Topic field: 500 character limit minimum (not 100).
Auto-save: Every form must auto-save as DRAFT every 30 seconds.
Show "Saved as draft" with timestamp in bottom-right of form.
Attachment upload:

Drag-and-drop zone: dashed border, centred upload icon, clear instruction text
After upload: immediately prompt for friendly name in an inline field
Show attachment list with: friendly name (bold), original filename (grey, small), file size, delete icon
Multiple attachments supported — list grows downward


