10. CONFIRMATION DIALOGS
Three types — use the right one:

Destructive confirmation (Return, Archive, Delete):

Title: "Return this agenda item?" (28px, red icon)
Body: "This will send the item back to [Wing Name] with your comments.
       The submitter will be notified."
Input: Comments field (required, minimum 10 chars)
Buttons: [Cancel] [Return Item]  ← red filled button

Consequential confirmation (Approve, Finalize, Submit):

Title: "Finalize this sitting?" (28px, gold icon)
Body: "This will lock all 14 agenda items. No new items can be added
       after finalization. Serial numbers will be assigned."
Checklist: ✓ 14 items consolidated  ✓ All wings notified
Buttons: [Cancel] [Finalize Sitting]  ← gold filled button

Simple confirmation (routine actions):

Title: "Approve agenda item?"
Buttons: [Cancel] [Approve]  ← blue filled button
RULE: Never silently execute a destructive action. Always confirm.

