Loading: Use MUI Skeleton — never spinners in the main content area.
jsx// Table loading
<Skeleton variant="rectangular" height={56} sx={{ mb: 1, borderRadius: 1 }} />
// Repeat 5x
Empty states: Custom illustration + helpful text + primary action.
Never show an empty table with just column headers.
[icon — e.g. clipboard]
No agenda items yet
