[+ Create Agenda Item]

14. NOTIFICATIONS
Notification bell in AppBar:

Shows unread count badge (red, max "99+")
Dropdown panel: last 10 notifications, 320px wide
Each notification: icon (type-based), title, timestamp, unread indicator
"Mark all read" link
Polling every 60 seconds (not WebSocket — simpler, more stable)

Toast notifications (MUI Snackbar):

Success: green, bottom-left, 4 second auto-dismiss
Error: red, bottom-left, stays until closed
Info: blue, bottom-left, 4 second auto-dismiss
Position: bottom-left (NOT top-right — top-right covers content)
Max 1 visible at a time. Queue subsequent toasts.


15. RESPONSIVE
This is primarily a desktop application but must not break on a 1024px wide laptop.

Sidebar: collapses to icons-only at < 1200px (not hidden — icon rail)
DataGrid: horizontal scroll on < 900px, not column removal
Cards: stack to single column on < 768px
PDF side panel: full-screen overlay on < 1024px
Minimum supported viewport: 1024px × 768px
